item.title: Netflix experiences streaming delays leading up to Tyson-Paul fight
item.description: Netflix’s first attempt at handling a live sports event did not receive a passing grade. Friday’s fight between Mike Tyson and Jake Paul experienced streaming problems according to many viewers on social media.

item.title: Forget downtown or the ’burbs. The far-flung exurbs are where people are moving
item.description: Not long ago, Polk County’s biggest draw was citrus. The Florida county produces more boxes of citrus than any other in the state.

item.title: Arizona state Senate candidate killed in a car crash a day after conceding
item.description: The Democratic candidate for an Arizona state Senate seat has been killed in a traffic accident the morning after conceding to his GOP rival.
